--- host ---
host | host6 hostname.

  Display the IP address of hostname. If hostname has several IP addresses, only
the first one is displayed. host6 allows IPv6 DNS lookup.

examples:
---------

  lsfw> host google.com
  google.com has address 74.125.230.78

  lsfw> host6 google.com
  google.com has address 2a00:1450:4007:800::1000
